Sentencas: By adding 1% Bi(2)O(3) (mol%) into LSCF (La(0.54)Sr(0.44)Co(0.2)Fe(0.8)O(3-delta)), a layer of dense LSCF film is introduced to the upside of yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte

Sentencas: The dense film increases the interface contact area and reduces the interface ion transfer resistance between cathode and electrolyte remarkably.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte

Sentencas: As a result, the cell performance is greatly elevated from 492 to 901 mW cm(-2) at 650 degrees C. Besides, on the basis of careful observation of the cathode surface by FE-SEM, the function of Bi(2)O(3) to promote the cathode sintering is speculated.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte

Sentencas: The Bi(2)O(3) and the LSCF come into being a kind of eutectic liquid.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte

Sentencas: The eutectic liquid flows down from the cathode bulk to the interface between the cathode and the electrolyte where it accumulates to form a dense layer.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte

Sentencas: This dense layer illuminates the function of adding Bi(2)O(3) into LSCF cathode.
Titulo: A high performance solid oxide fuel cells operating at intermediate temperature with a modified interface between cathode and electrolyte
